57
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:15,400
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Mozart.

58
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:20,200
<font size=24>我可以想到当时他的名字随时随地在我心中响起</font>
I can't think of a time when I didn't know his name.

59
