<font size=24>你娶她那样的人也不足为奇</font>
No other reason why you'd marry someone like that.

436
00:49:07,610 --> 00:49:09,070
<font size=24>请进</font>
Come in.

437
00:49:11,900 --> 00:49:15,700
<font size=24>抱歉  妈妈的身体不是很舒服</font>
Excuse me. Wolfie, Mom isn't feeling very well.

438
00:49:15,910 --> 00:49:17,570
<font size=24>我们能回家吗?  好的</font>
-Can we go home? -Yes.

439
00:49:17,820 --> 00:49:21,040
<font size=24>不  你现在不能带他走</font>
No, no, no. You can't take him away now.

440
00:49:21,240 --> 00:49:24,040
<font size=24>今晚是属于他的</font>
This is his night.

441
00:49:24,210 --> 00:49:26,830
<font size=24>莫扎特  你不给我们介绍一下?</font>
Won't you introduce us, Wolfgang?

442
00:49:27,040 --> 00:49:30,710
<font size=24>对不起  晚安</font>
Excuse us, Fr?ulein. Good night, signore.

443
00:49:32,210 --> 00:49:37,390
<font size=24>在那个时候我就知道</font>
At that moment I knew, beyond any doubt...

444
00:49:37,550 --> 00:49:39,640
<font size=24>他掌握了她</font>
he'd had her.

445
00:49:39,890 --> 00:49:43,390
<font size=24>那家伙夺走了我亲爱的女人</font>
The creature had had my darling girl.

446
00:49:51,070 --> 00:49:53,730
<font size=24>真是难以令人了解!</font>
It was incomprehensible!

447
00:49:54,240 --> 00:49:56,900
<font size=24>上帝的旨意为何?</font>
What was God up to?

448
00:49:58,240 --> 00:50:01,410
<font size=24>我有可能去尝试吗?</font>
Was it possible I was being tested?

449
00:50:02,450 --> 00:50:07,080
<font size=24>上帝期望我得到原谅</font>
Was God expecting me to offer forgiveness...

450
00:50:07,290 --> 00:50:10,080
<font size=24>在面对所有事的时候吗?</font>
in the face of every offense?

451
00:50:10,290 --> 00:50:12,130
<font size=24>不管有多痛苦?</font>
No matter how painful?

452
00:50:14,420 --> 00:50:16,420
<font size=24>这是非常有可能的</font>
It's very possible.

453
00:50:16,880 --> 00:50:19,090
<font size=24>但为何是他?</font>
But why him?

454
00:50:19,930 --> 00:50:25,310
<font size=24>为何选择莫扎特来教我谦卑呢?</font>
Why choose Mozart to teach me lessons in humility?

455
00:50:26,020 --> 00:50:31,150
<font size=24>我心中对那年轻人充满恨意</font>
My heart was filling up...with such hatred for that little man.

456
00:50:32,940 --> 00:50:36,440
<font size=24>因此我一生中第一次</font>
For the first time in my life, I began to know...

457
00:50:36,610 --> 00:50:41,120
<font size=24>心中有了残暴的想法</font>
really...violent thoughts.

458
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:47,410
<font size=24>每天  有时好几个小时  我会祈祷</font>
Every day, sometimes for hours, I would pray.

459
00:50:48,670 --> 00:50:50,210
<font size=24>上帝</font>
Lord...

460
00:50:51,420 --> 00:50:52,960
<font size=24>求求你</font>
please...

461
00:50:54,050 --> 00:50:55,840
<font size=24>送他</font>
send him away...

462
00:50:56,050 --> 00:50:58,800
<font size=24>回沙兹堡</font>
back to Salzburg.

463
00:51:00,640 --> 00:51:02,970
<font size=24>他的原因</font>
For his sake...

464
00:51:03,720 --> 00:51:06,220
<font size=24>也是我的原因</font>
as well as mine.

465
00:51:08,140 --> 00:51:12,230
<font size=24>-不  我不要他回来  -尊敬的阁下</font>
-No! I won't have him back. -But, Your Grace

466
00:51:12,480 --> 00:51:17,820
<font size=24>你儿子是被宠坏又任性的坏孩子</font>
Your son is an unprincipled, spoiled, conceited brat!

467
00:51:19,200 --> 00:51:24,160
<font size=24>我承认  这是事实</font>
Yes, sir...that is the truth.

468
00:51:25,660 --> 00:51:30,660
<font size=24>但是不要责怪他  这全都是我的错</font>
But don't blame him. The fault is mine, entirely.

469
00:51:30,830 --> 00:51:33,830
<font size=24>我是太溺爱他了</font>
I was too indulgent with him.

470
00:51:34,460 --> 00:51:37,340
<font size=24>求求您  陛下</font>
Please, Your Grace?

471
00:51:38,090 --> 00:51:40,340
<font size=24>再给他一次机会?</font>
Give him one more chance?

472
00:51:41,510 --> 00:51:44,010
<font size=24>好吧  你可以再试试看</font>
You have leave to try.

473
00:51:44,220 --> 00:51:48,390
<font size=24>谢谢你  谢谢</font>
God bless, Your Grace! I thank Your Grace.

474
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:50,560
<font size=24>我有紧急的事要告诉你</font>
I thank you!

475
00:51:54,270 --> 00:51:58,690
<font size=24>我要来维也纳了</font>
I write to you with urgent news. I'm coming to Vienna.

476
00:51:58,860 --> 00:52:02,740
<font size=24>直到你我见面之前...不准结婚</font>
Take no further steps towards marriage until we meet.

477
00:52:02,990 --> 00:52:07,080
<font size=24>若你尊敬一生尽心为你设想的父亲</font>
As you honor the father who has devoted his life to yours...

478
00:52:07,290 --> 00:52:10,200
<font size=24>就照我说的去作  并等我的到来</font>
do as I bid, and await my coming.

479
00:52:23,720 --> 00:52:27,600
<font size=24>现在我见证你们结成神圣的婚姻关系.</font>
I now join you in the holy bonds of matrimony.

480
00:52:28,600 --> 00:52:31,390
<font size=24>上帝与你们同在</font>
Those whom God hath joined together...

481
00:52:31,600 --> 00:52:34,650
<font size=24>使你们永远不分离</font>
let no man put asunder.

482
00:52:48,240 --> 00:52:49,580
<font size=24>敬爱的父亲  记得你说过</font>
Beloved father:

483
00:52:49,790 --> 00:52:55,290
<font size=24>维也纳是音乐家之都  征服这里  就等于征服全欧</font>
You say Vienna is the musicians' city. To conquer here is to conquer Europe.

484
00:52:55,540 --> 00:52:59,300
<font size=24>有妻相伴  我们必能成功 有朝一日我功成名就</font>
With my wife, I can do it. One day, when I'm wealthy...

485
00:52:59,550 --> 00:53:02,970
<font size=24>你可以过来和我们一起住  我们会非常快乐</font>
you'll live with us, and we'll be so happy.

486
00:53:13,440 --> 00:53:17,270
<font size=24>早安  宫廷作曲家  这是我侄女  伊丽莎白公主</font>
Good morning. This is my niece, Princess Elizabeth.

487
00:53:17,440 --> 00:53:18,690
<font size=24>尊贵的殿下</font>
Your Highness.

488
00:53:18,940 --> 00:53:22,280
<font size=24>她请我推荐给她一合适音乐教师</font>
She's asked me to recommend a music instructor.

489
00:53:22,440 --> 00:53:26,200
<font size=24>-我想我己有一个很好的构想  -陛下!</font>
-I've come up with an excellent idea. -Your Majesty!

490
00:53:26,450 --> 00:53:29,330
<font size=24>那真是我的荣幸</font>
It would be such a tremendous honor!

491
00:53:29,580 --> 00:53:33,830
<font size=24>我想到莫扎特  你觉得如何?</font>
I was thinking of Herr Mozart. What is your view?

492
00:53:35,330 --> 00:53:38,630
<font size=24>那倒是个不错的主意  但是陛下...</font>
It's an interesting idea, Majesty, but....

493
00:53:39,880 --> 00:53:41,590
<font size=24>什么?</font>
Yes?

494
00:53:41,960 --> 00:53:49,470
<font size=24>我所关切是要使您免受任何因偏袒而受到的伤害</font>
My concern is to protect you...from any hint of favoritism.

495
00:53:54,100 --> 00:53:55,600
<font size=24>偏袒?</font>
Favoritism.

496
00:53:55,810 --> 00:53:58,400
<font size=24>-怎么了  大臣?  -什么怎么了</font>
-What is this? -What is what?

497
00:53:58,650 --> 00:54:04,490
<font size=24>当个13岁女孩的教师 还得把作品交给某些呆子委员会审查?</font>
Why must I submit samples of my work to a committee to teach a girl?

498
00:54:04,650 --> 00:54:07,400
<font size=24>因为这是陛下的旨意</font>
Because His Majesty wishes it.

499
00:54:08,490 --> 00:54:10,870
<font size=24>陛下在生我的气?</font>
Is the emperor angry with me?

500
00:54:11,120 --> 00:54:15,500
<font size=24>-刚好相反  -那他为何不指派我?</font>
-Quite the contrary. -Then why not appoint me to the post?

501
00:54:15,710 --> 00:54:18,920
<font size=24>莫扎特  维也纳作曲家不只你一人</font>
You are not the only composer in Vienna.

502
00:54:19,170 --> 00:54:22,420
<font size=24>没错  但我却是其中最好的</font>
No. But I'm the best.

503
00:54:23,340 --> 00:54:25,260
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Mozart.

504
00:54:26,510 --> 00:54:30,180
<font size=24>谦虚一点对你会更有益</font>
A little modesty might suit you better.

505
00:54:37,270 --> 00:54:39,270
<font size=24>委员会有哪些人?</font>
Who is on this committee?

506
00:54:39,690 --> 00:54:44,360
<font size=24>卡普麦斯特  罗林保伯爵  还有宫廷作曲家</font>
Kapellmeister Bonno, Count Orsini-Rosenberg and Salieri.

507
00:54:44,530 --> 00:54:49,070
<font size=24>一想即知  意大利人  当然  总是意大利人</font>
Naturally, the Italians! Of course, always the Italians!

508
00:54:49,530 --> 00:54:52,070
<font size=24>他们全是不了解音乐的白痴</font>
They're all musical idiots!

509
00:54:53,030 --> 00:54:58,540
<font size=24>-你要他们审核我的作品  -年轻人</font>
-And you want them to judge my music? -Young man...

510
00:54:58,710 --> 00:55:02,710
<font size=24>问题很简单  若你想得到这职位</font>
the issue is quite simple. If you want this position...

511
00:55:02,920 --> 00:55:07,380
<font size=24>必须拿出作品和其它作曲家一起送审</font>
you must submit your stuff, along with all your colleagues.

512
00:55:07,550 --> 00:55:09,430
<font size=24>一定要吗?</font>
-Must I? -Mm-hm.

513
00:55:10,930 --> 00:55:11,970
<font size=24>可惜我作不到</font>
Well, I won't.

514
00:55:12,890 --> 00:55:15,390
<font size=24>这样的日子我们怎么过?</font>
How are we supposed to live?

515
00:55:16,980 --> 00:55:19,810
<font size=24>要我在大街上乞讨吗?</font>
Do you want me to beg on the streets?

516
00:55:20,060 --> 00:55:22,060
<font size=24>别傻了</font>
Don't be stupid.

517
00:55:22,810 --> 00:55:25,900
<font size=24>-他们想看到的只是你的作品  -糟糕</font>
-All they want to see is your work. -Shit.

518
00:55:26,070 --> 00:55:30,990
<font size=24>你是怎么啦?  闭嘴!  给我闭嘴</font>
-What's wrong with that? -Shut up! Just shut up.

519
00:55:31,240 --> 00:55:35,490
<font size=24>一个王室学生  整个维也纳都会感到震惊的</font>
One royal pupil, and all of Vienna will come flocking.

520
00:55:35,740 --> 00:55:37,910
<font size=24>他们什么都会</font>
They'll come anyway.

521
00:55:38,460 --> 00:55:42,080
<font size=24>不  他们不会的  他们喜欢我在这</font>
-No, they won't. -They love me here.

522
00:55:42,290 --> 00:55:47,090
<font size=24>-我对这个城市很清楚  -你是万事通,对吧!</font>
-I know how things work in this city. -You know everything, don't you?

523
00:56:15,620 --> 00:56:17,280
<font size=24>-什么事?  -抱歉  先生</font>
-Yes? -Excuse me, sir.

524
00:56:17,490 --> 00:56:20,450
<font size=24>-有位小姐坚持要见您  -是谁?</font>
-A lady insists on talking to you. -Who?

525
00:56:20,660 --> 00:56:24,250
<font size=24>她没说  只是说有急事</font>
She didn't say, but she says it's urgent.

526
00:56:26,460 --> 00:56:28,630
<font size=24>失陪  亲爱的</font>
Excuse me, my dear.

527
00:56:36,760 --> 00:56:38,970
<font size=24>我能帮你什么忙?</font>
How can I help you?

528
00:56:43,980 --> 00:56:47,980
<font size=24>-莫扎特夫人?  -我是为了我丈夫来的</font>
-Frau Mozart? -I've come on behalf of my husband.

529
00:56:48,190 --> 00:56:53,820
<font size=24>我带他部分作品  让他更有机会得到皇室的工作</font>
I brought samples of his work so he can be considered for the appointment.

530
00:56:55,490 --> 00:56:59,580
<font size=24>真是太好了  可是他为何不自己来?</font>
How charming, but why did he not come himself?

531
00:57:01,200 --> 00:57:04,160
<font size=24>先生  他非常的忙</font>
Well, he's terribly busy, sir.

532
00:57:07,590 --> 00:57:09,000
<font size=24>我知道</font>
I understand.

533
00:57:11,510 --> 00:57:14,680
<font size=24>当然我一有空就会看</font>
I will look at them the moment I can.

534
00:57:14,880 --> 00:57:19,300
<font size=24>这是我的荣幸  请向他致以我最温暖的问候</font>
It will be an honor. Please give him my warmest regards.

535
00:57:19,510 --> 00:57:23,850
<font size=24>如果你现在就看会不会太麻烦?</font>
Would it be too much trouble to ask you to look at them now?

536
00:57:24,190 --> 00:57:30,570
<font size=24>-我在这里等  -现在恐怕...没空</font>
-While I wait. -I'm afraid I'm not at leisure...this precise moment.

537
00:57:30,820 --> 00:57:34,700
<font size=24>就先放我这儿  我保证很安全</font>
Leave them with me. I assure you, they will be safe.

538
00:57:35,700 --> 00:57:38,740
<font size=24>我恐怕不能这么作</font>
I really cannot do that, sir.

539
00:57:39,410 --> 00:57:42,870
<font size=24>事实是  他不知我来这里</font>
You see, he doesn't know I'm here.

540
00:57:44,580 --> 00:57:47,040
<font size=24>他没叫你来?</font>
Then he didn't send you?

541
00:57:47,250 --> 00:57:50,920
<font size=24>是我自作主张</font>
No, sir. This was my own idea.

542
00:57:53,340 --> 00:57:57,050
<font size=24>-我知道了  -先生  我们穷途末路了</font>
-I see. -Sir, we're desperate.

543
00:57:57,970 --> 00:58:01,050
<font size=24>我们真的需要这份工作</font>
We really need this job.

544
00:58:01,260 --> 00:58:04,890
<font size=24>我先生入不敷出</font>
My husband spends far more than he can ever earn.

545
00:58:05,060 --> 00:58:09,400
<font size=24>我不是说他懒情  他一点也不懒  他整天都在工作</font>
I don't mean that he's lazy, because he works all day long.

546
00:58:09,610 --> 00:58:14,070
<font size=24>只是...他不实际</font>
It's just that he's not practical.

547
00:58:14,400 --> 00:58:18,570
<font size=24>他就是守不住钱  这真是太可笑了</font>
Money simply slips through his fingers. It's ridiculous.

548
00:58:21,660 --> 00:58:24,410
<font size=24>要不要吃些东西</font>
Let me offer you some refreshment.

549
00:58:24,620 --> 00:58:26,960
<font size=24>你知道这是什么吗?</font>
Do you know what these are?

550
00:58:28,630 --> 00:58:32,090
<font size=24>维纳斯的乳头</font>
Capezzoli di Venere! Nipples of Venus.

551
00:58:33,090 --> 00:58:38,090
<font size=24>这是包白兰地糖的核桃  吃一个吧</font>
They're Roman chestnuts in brandied sugar. Try one. Go on!

552
00:58:38,260 --> 00:58:40,800
<font size=24>你一定会吓一跳</font>
They're quite surprising.

553
00:58:45,640 --> 00:58:47,600
<font size=24>很完美</font>
They're wonderful!

554
00:58:49,600 --> 00:58:52,610
<font size=24>多谢你了  先生</font>
Thank you very much, Your Excellency.

555
00:58:52,770 --> 00:58:55,440
<font size=24>别那么称呼我</font>
Don't keep calling me that.

556
00:58:56,280 --> 00:58:58,950
<font size=24>这样子有距离感</font>
Keeps me at such a distance.

557
00:58:59,660 --> 00:59:02,780
<font size=24>我不是生下来就当宫廷作曲家</font>
I wasn't born a court composer, you know.

558
00:59:02,990 --> 00:59:05,120
<font size=24>我来自一个小镇</font>
I'm from a small town.

559
00:59:05,330 --> 00:59:07,450
<font size=24>正和你先生一样</font>
Just like your husband.

560
00:59:09,960 --> 00:59:12,790
<font size=24>你确定你不能留下这些资料</font>
Are you sure you can't...

561
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:16,670
<font size=24>改天再来?</font>
leave this and come back again?

562
00:59:17,840 --> 00:59:20,800
<font size=24>听来很不错</font>
It's very tempting, sir.

563
00:59:20,970 --> 00:59:24,300
<font size=24>不过恐怕不行</font>
But it's impossible, I'm afraid.

564
00:59:24,680 --> 00:59:27,850
<font size=24>若他发现这些不见了  一定会发疯的</font>
He'd be frantic if he knew they were missing.

565
00:59:28,060 --> 00:59:30,940
<font size=24>这些都是原稿</font>
You see, they're all originals.

566
00:59:31,810 --> 00:59:35,190
<font size=24>-原稿?  -是的  他从来不会复写</font>
-Originals? -Yes, sir. He doesn't make copies.

567
00:59:46,950 --> 00:59:50,370
<font size=24>这些全是原稿?</font>
These...are originals?

568
01:00:26,870 --> 01:00:28,370
<font size=24>太不可思议了!</font>
Astounding!

569
01:00:28,870 --> 01:00:32,370
<font size=24>简直不敢相信!</font>
It was actually. It was beyond belief.

570
01:00:33,120 --> 01:00:35,750
<font size=24>这些乐稿全是唯一的版本</font>
These were first and only...

571
01:00:36,380 --> 01:00:38,550
<font size=24>全然没有任何修改的痕迹</font>
drafts of music.

572
01:00:39,800 --> 01:00:45,390
<font size=24>一点也没有</font>
But they showed no corrections of any kind. Not one.

573
01:00:48,220 --> 01:00:51,560
<font size=24>他只是将在脑中已完成的曲调</font>
He had simply written down music...

574
01:00:51,730 --> 01:00:54,730
<font size=24>一成不变的写下来而巳</font>
already finished in his head.

575
01:00:55,020 --> 01:01:00,530
<font size=24>一页接着一页如同是在听写一般</font>
Page after page of it. As if he were just taking dictation.

576
01:01:07,240 --> 01:01:13,460
<font size=24>这是前所未见的悦耳音乐</font>
And music...finished as no music is ever finished.

577
01:01:16,580 --> 01:01:22,300
<font size=24>更动任何一个音符就不完美</font>
Displace one note...and there would be diminishment.

578
01:01:23,550 --> 01:01:27,760
<font size=24>更动一小节  结构性就会瓦解</font>
Displace one phrase, and the structure would fall.

579
01:01:31,430 --> 01:01:33,980
<font size=24>我现在了解...</font>
It was clear to me...

580
01:01:34,560 --> 01:01:38,560
<font size=24>那夜在大主教家中听到的音乐</font>
that sound I had heard in the archbishop's palace...

