882
01:30:32,920 --> 01:30:35,170
<font size=24>他写些什么?</font>
What is it he's writing?

883
01:30:38,180 --> 01:30:40,760
<font size=24>这个我不知道  先生</font>
I wouldn't know that, sir.

884
01:30:40,970 --> 01:30:42,760
<font size=24>当然你不明白!</font>
Of course not.

885
01:30:42,970 --> 01:30:44,980
<font size=24>你是个乖女孩</font>
You're a good girl.

886
01:30:45,180 --> 01:30:47,600
<font size=24>你为我这么做太好了</font>
You're very kind to do this.

887
01:30:47,810 --> 01:30:53,020
<font size=24>下次他不在家时  让我知道一下</font>
The next time you're sure they'll be out of the house, let me know.

888
01:30:59,320 --> 01:31:01,870
<font size=24>谢谢</font>
Thank you, sir.

889
01:32:41,130 --> 01:32:44,510
<font size=24>我想我知道他如何生活了</font>
I think I found out about the money, sir.

890
01:32:45,300 --> 01:32:47,810
<font size=24>怎么说?</font>
Yes? What?

891
01:32:48,060 --> 01:32:53,060
<font size=24>他这里有七个鼻烟盒我发誓这全都是纯金的</font>
He kept seven snuffboxes in here. I could swear they were all gold.

892
01:32:53,520 --> 01:32:55,560
<font size=24>你看</font>
And now look.

893
01:32:55,770 --> 01:32:57,900
<font size=24>现在只剩一个了</font>
There's only one left.

894
01:32:58,990 --> 01:33:01,400
<font size=24>他在哪里工作?</font>
Where does he work?

895
01:33:02,910 --> 01:33:05,160
<font size=24>在里边  先生</font>
In there, sir.

896
01:33:50,540 --> 01:33:54,000
<font size=24>先生们  我刚刚听说了些消息...</font>
Gentlemen, I've just heard some news...

897
01:33:54,370 --> 01:33:57,500
<font size=24>-可能各位会感兴趣  -什么新闻?</font>
-that may interest you. -What?

898
01:33:57,710 --> 01:34:02,090
<font size=24>莫扎特在写新歌剧  意大利语的</font>
Mozart is writing a new opera. An Italian opera.

899
01:34:02,590 --> 01:34:04,720
<font size=24>意大利语?</font>
Italian?

900
01:34:05,510 --> 01:34:09,720
<font size=24>还不止这样  他选费加洛做为主角</font>
That's not all. He has chosen for his subject, Figaro.

901
01:34:10,390 --> 01:34:13,180
<font size=24>《费加洛婚礼》!</font>
The Marriage of Figaro.

902
01:34:13,390 --> 01:34:16,900
<font size=24>他将那种剧本写曲子?</font>
He's setting that play to music?

903
01:34:17,360 --> 01:34:18,610
<font size=24>是啊!</font>
Yes.

904
01:34:19,860 --> 01:34:23,320
<font size=24>这《费加洛婚礼》是什么剧本</font>
What is this Marriage of Figaro?

905
01:34:23,530 --> 01:34:26,990
<font size=24>那是一出法国的戏剧</font>
It's a French play, Kapellmeister.

906
01:34:27,200 --> 01:34:30,410
<font size=24>是陛下禁止上演的</font>
It has been banned by the emperor.

907
01:34:30,620 --> 01:34:32,660
<font size=24>你确定吗?</font>
You're absolutely sure?

908
01:34:36,250 --> 01:34:38,580
<font size=24>莫扎特先生</font>
Herr Mozart.

909
01:34:39,540 --> 01:34:41,670
<font size=24>大家坐下</font>
Gentlemen, sit down.

910
01:34:46,430 --> 01:34:48,130
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Mozart.

911
01:34:49,390 --> 01:34:56,730
<font size=24>你可知我已经宣布法国戏剧《费加洛婚礼》不得体</font>
Are you aware that I have declared the French play Figaro...unsuitable for our theater?

912
01:34:57,900 --> 01:34:59,690
<font size=24>是  我知道</font>
Yes, sire.

913
01:34:59,900 --> 01:35:05,070
<font size=24>我们听说你在写这出歌剧是不是事实?</font>
Yet we hear you're making an opera from it. Is this true?

914
01:35:08,700 --> 01:35:10,910
<font size=24>谁告诉你的?  陛下</font>
Who told you this, Majesty?

915
01:35:11,120 --> 01:35:15,790
<font size=24>你现在没有资格问问题  是不是事实?</font>
It is not your place to ask questions. Is it true?

916
01:35:15,960 --> 01:35:17,960
<font size=24>-是真的吗?</font>
Yes, I....

917
01:35:18,420 --> 01:35:20,710
<font size=24>-是的  我承认</font>
I admit it is.

918
01:35:22,800 --> 01:35:25,300
<font size=24>你可不可以告诉我为什么?</font>
Would you tell me why?

919
01:35:27,380 --> 01:35:29,800
<font size=24>陛下  那只是个喜剧</font>
Majesty, it is only a comedy.

920
01:35:30,050 --> 01:35:32,800
<font size=24>你怎么想并不重要  莫扎特</font>
What you think is scarcely the point.

921
01:35:33,060 --> 01:35:36,810
<font size=24>陛下的想法才重要</font>
It's what His Majesty thinks that counts.

922
01:35:37,140 --> 01:35:39,190
<font size=24>可是  陛下</font>
But, Your Majesty

923
01:35:39,400 --> 01:35:41,270
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Mozart...

924
01:35:41,480 --> 01:35:43,690
<font size=24>我是宽大的人</font>
I am a tolerant man.

925
01:35:43,900 --> 01:35:48,820
<font size=24>我不会随便下禁令的  我决定的事都有理由</font>
I do not censor things lightly. When I do, I have good reason.

926
01:35:49,700 --> 01:35:52,700
<font size=24>《费加洛婚礼》是不好的戏剧</font>
Figaro is a bad play.

927
01:35:53,330 --> 01:35:55,990
<font size=24>因为它挑动阶级之间的仇视</font>
It stirs up hatred between classes.

928
01:35:56,250 --> 01:35:59,290
<font size=24>法国就是一例</font>
In France, it has caused only bitterness.

929
01:35:59,500 --> 01:36:04,840
<font size=24>我的亲妹妹安东妮写信给我  说她现在很害怕自己的子民</font>
My sister Antoinette is beginning to be frightened of her own people.

930
01:36:05,000 --> 01:36:08,630
<font size=24>陛下  我对你发誓歌剧已经没有那些成分</font>
I swear, there's nothing like that in the piece.

931
01:36:08,840 --> 01:36:13,760
<font size=24>我把这些都删掉了  我讨厌政治</font>
I've taken out everything that could give offense. I hate politics.

932
01:36:13,970 --> 01:36:16,510
<font size=24>我想你太天真了</font>
I'm afraid you're rather innocent.

933
01:36:16,720 --> 01:36:21,850
<font size=24>在这个动荡时期  我不能冒险让它...</font>
In these dangerous times I cannot afford to provoke our people...

934
01:36:22,020 --> 01:36:24,360
<font size=24>刺激贵族或平民的情绪</font>
simply over a theater piece.

935
01:36:24,610 --> 01:36:29,650
<font size=24>陛下  那只是个谈情说爱的喜剧</font>
Majesty, this is just a frolic. A piece about love.

936
01:36:29,860 --> 01:36:31,860
<font size=24>又是爱情</font>
"Love." Again!

937
01:36:32,240 --> 01:36:33,870
<font size=24>而且是最新潮的</font>
And it's new!

938
01:36:34,120 --> 01:36:38,160
<font size=24>很新  人们会为它而疯迷的</font>
It's entirely new. The people will go mad for it.

939
01:36:38,370 --> 01:36:40,620
<font size=24>我举例说明</font>
I have scenes....

940
01:36:41,370 --> 01:36:43,880
<font size=24>例如第二幕的最后</font>
The end of Act II, for example.

941
01:36:44,040 --> 01:36:48,050
<font size=24>一开始是夫妻吵嘴的对唱</font>
It starts as a duet. A husband and wife quarreling.

942
01:36:48,300 --> 01:36:53,380
<font size=24>突然有阴谋的女佣跑进来  非常有趣的情景</font>
Suddenly, the scheming maid comes in. It's a very funny situation.

943
01:36:53,640 --> 01:36:55,470
<font size=24>二重唱转成三重唱</font>
Duet turns into trio.

944
01:36:55,680 --> 01:36:58,560
<font size=24>然后先生的侍者走进来他与女佣有阴谋</font>
Then the husband's valet comes in.

945
01:36:58,770 --> 01:37:00,560
<font size=24>三重唱变成四重唱</font>
Trio turns into quartet.

946
01:37:00,770 --> 01:37:03,730
<font size=24>然后愚蠢的园丁跑进来四重唱成为五重唱</font>
Then a gardener. Quartet becomes quintet.

947
01:37:03,900 --> 01:37:05,900
<font size=24>然后继续变成...</font>
And so on, on and on.

948
01:37:06,150 --> 01:37:08,730
<font size=24>六重唱  七重唱  八重唱</font>
Sextet, septet, octet.

949
01:37:08,900 --> 01:37:12,700
<font size=24>陛下你猜我能这样维持多久?</font>
How long do you think I can sustain that?

950
01:37:13,490 --> 01:37:14,910
<font size=24>我不知道</font>
I have no idea.

951
01:37:15,160 --> 01:37:16,530
<font size=24>猜看看</font>
Guess.

952
01:37:17,490 --> 01:37:18,910
<font size=24>猜看看  陛下</font>
Guess, Your Majesty.

953
01:37:19,160 --> 01:37:24,170
<font size=24>猜猜看这种过程可以维持多久然后再将它加一倍</font>
Imagine the longest time it could be sustained, then double it.

954
01:37:25,000 --> 01:37:29,590
<font size=24>恩...六分钟?</font>
Well....Six...

955
01:37:30,420 --> 01:37:32,720
<font size=24>七分钟?</font>
seven minutes?

956
01:37:35,430 --> 01:37:39,850
<font size=24>-八分钟?  -二十分钟  陛下</font>
-Eight minutes? -Twenty, sire. Twenty minutes!

957
01:37:40,060 --> 01:37:44,390
<font size=24>二十分钟不断的音乐  完全没有对白</font>
Twenty minutes of continuous music. No recitatives!

958
01:37:44,850 --> 01:37:47,230
<font size=24>只有在歌剧里可以这样处理</font>
Sire, only opera can do this.

959
01:37:47,440 --> 01:37:51,360
<font size=24>戏剧中如果二人以上同时说话</font>
In a play, if more than one person speaks at once...

960
01:37:51,570 --> 01:37:53,530
<font size=24>就只剩下噪音  没有人听得懂</font>
it's just noise.

961
01:37:53,740 --> 01:37:56,280
<font size=24>但在歌剧中  伴随着音乐</font>
But with opera, with music...

962
01:37:56,450 --> 01:38:00,620
<font size=24>二十人同时说话</font>
you can have 20 individuals all talking at the same time.

963
01:38:00,870 --> 01:38:03,870
<font size=24>但不是噪音  而是完美的旋律</font>
It's not noise. It's a perfect harmony!

964
01:38:04,290 --> 01:38:07,420
<font size=24>莫扎特  我们不是在谈音乐</font>
Mozart, music is not the issue here.

965
01:38:07,630 --> 01:38:12,920
<font size=24>没有人怀疑你的才能  我们是在讨论你所选的素材</font>
No one doubts your talent. It's your literary judgment that's in question.

966
01:38:13,130 --> 01:38:19,140
<font size=24>就算没有政治的成份  它仍是一个低俗的剧本</font>
Even without the politics, it would remain a vulgar farce.

967
01:38:19,390 --> 01:38:22,220
<font size=24>不要将你的才能浪费在废料上</font>
Why waste your spirit on such rubbish?

968
01:38:22,430 --> 01:38:26,480
<font size=24>你可以选些更高级的剧本</font>
Surely you can choose more elevated themes.

969
01:38:26,650 --> 01:38:29,860
<font size=24>高级的!  高级!  那是什么意思</font>
Elevated! What does that mean, elevated?

970
01:38:30,070 --> 01:38:33,820
<font size=24>我给这些高级的东西烦死了</font>
I am fed to the teeth with these...

971
01:38:33,990 --> 01:38:37,280
<font size=24>全都是古老  没有生命力的传说</font>
elevated things. Old dead legends.

972
01:38:37,490 --> 01:38:41,620
<font size=24>为何我们一定要不断的只去写有关神的传说?</font>
Why must we go on forever writing of gods and legends?

973
01:38:41,830 --> 01:38:46,830
<font size=24>因为神是不朽的</font>
Because they do. They go on forever.

974
01:38:47,580 --> 01:38:51,500
<font size=24>至少他们代表我们心中的永恒</font>
At least what they represent: the eternal in us.

975
01:38:51,750 --> 01:38:54,510
<font size=24>歌剧是为了使我们更高尚的  莫扎特</font>
Opera is here to ennoble us, Mozart.

976
01:38:54,670 --> 01:38:57,800
<font size=24>就如同你我及陛下是高尚的一样</font>
You and me, just the same as His Majesty.

977
01:38:58,010 --> 01:39:01,350
<font size=24>说得好!  公爵</font>
Bello. Veramente.

978
01:39:02,100 --> 01:39:06,850
<font size=24>为何要高尚  大家诚实一点</font>
"Bello, bello, bello." Come on now, be honest!

979
01:39:07,020 --> 01:39:12,690
<font size=24>你们谁不是比较爱听理发师的话  而不喜欢大力士神话?</font>
You'd rather listen to your hairdresser than Hercules, Horatius or Orpheus.

980
01:39:12,940 --> 01:39:16,990
<font size=24>或是那些大家祟拜的诸神  这些崇高的人连大便都是大理石</font>
People so lofty, they sound as if they shit marble!

981
01:39:17,780 --> 01:39:19,490
<font size=24>什么!</font>
What!

982
01:39:19,870 --> 01:39:23,910
<font size=24>注意你的用词!  莫扎特你太放肆了!</font>
Govern your tongue, Mozart! How dare you!

983
01:39:28,370 --> 01:39:31,210
<font size=24>原谅我  陛下</font>
Forgive me, Majesty.

984
01:39:32,420 --> 01:39:34,840
<font size=24>我是个低俗的人</font>
I'm a vulgar man...

985
01:39:35,050 --> 01:39:38,220
<font size=24>但我保证我的音乐绝不低俗</font>
but I assure you, my music is not.

986
01:39:41,890 --> 01:39:45,060
<font size=24>你是很有热情的人  莫扎特</font>
You are passionate, Mozart...

987
01:39:45,310 --> 01:39:49,230
<font size=24>但你并不能说服我们</font>
but you do not persuade.

988
01:39:51,730 --> 01:39:55,570
<font size=24>陛下  整个歌剧已经完成了</font>
Sire, the whole opera is finished.

989
01:39:55,860 --> 01:39:59,070
<font size=24>你知道我花了多少心血</font>
Do you know how much work went into it?

990
01:39:59,410 --> 01:40:04,740
<font size=24>陛下已经没有耐心了!</font>
His Majesty has been more than patient, signore.

991
01:40:05,910 --> 01:40:09,160
<font size=24>不让我演给你看  如何能说服你</font>
How can I persuade if I can't show it?

992
01:40:09,370 --> 01:40:12,420
<font size=24>够了  莫扎特先生</font>
That will do, Herr Mozart.

993
01:40:14,250 --> 01:40:17,170
<font size=24>就让我告诉你序幕是怎样好了</font>
Just let me tell you how it begins.

994
01:40:17,380 --> 01:40:21,260
<font size=24>我可不可以这么做  陛下?  只是提一下开头</font>
May I just do that, Majesty? Show you how it begins? Just that?

995
01:40:26,770 --> 01:40:28,100
<font size=24>好!</font>
Please.

996
01:40:29,100 --> 01:40:30,940
<font size=24>请看</font>
Look....

997
01:40:31,230 --> 01:40:34,690
<font size=24>有个佣人跪在地上您知道为什么吗?</font>
There's a servant on his knees. Do you know why?

998
01:40:34,900 --> 01:40:38,280
<font size=24>不是因为任何人要他那样  是因为他在测量</font>
Not from oppression. He's measuring a space.

999
01:40:38,530 --> 01:40:40,570
<font size=24>你知道测量什么吗?</font>
Do you know what for?

1000
01:40:40,780 --> 01:40:43,490
<font size=24>他结婚用的床</font>
His bed. His wedding bed.

1001
01:40:43,700 --> 01:40:45,990
<font size=24>看看是否放得下</font>
To see if it will fit!

1002
01:41:19,820 --> 01:41:23,570
<font size=24>莫扎特已经开始彩排了</font>
Well, Mozart is already rehearsing.

1003
01:41:28,660 --> 01:41:31,910
<font size=24>既然如此  各位那我们该</font>
In that case, gentlemen, I think....

1004
01:41:36,040 --> 01:41:39,170
<font size=24>尽一切可能的帮助他</font>
I think we should help Mozart all we can.

1005
01:41:42,470 --> 01:41:45,680
<font size=24>让他不要激怒陛下</font>
And protect him against the emperor's anger.

1006
01:41:45,930 --> 01:41:47,800
<font size=24>什么处份?</font>
What anger?

1007
01:41:48,010 --> 01:41:50,260
<font size=24>因为芭雷舞啊!</font>
About the ballet.

1008
01:41:50,970 --> 01:41:53,310
<font size=24>什么芭雷舞?</font>
What ballet?

1009
01:41:53,770 --> 01:42:01,360
<font size=24>陛下不是禁止芭雷舞出现在歌剧</font>
Excuse me...but didn't His Majesty specifically forbid the ballet in his opera?

1010
01:42:36,230 --> 01:42:37,650
<font size=24>莫扎特!</font>
Mozart!

1011
01:42:38,480 --> 01:42:40,820
<font size=24>什么事?</font>
-Herr Mozart! -Yes?

1012
01:42:41,020 --> 01:42:44,150
<font size=24>可不可以借一步说话!  当然可以  院长先生!</font>
-A word with you.  Certainly, Herr Direktor.

1013
01:42:44,360 --> 01:42:46,240
<font size=24>现在!  现在!</font>
Now, Herr Mozart!

1014
01:42:47,200 --> 01:42:49,070
<font size=24>休息五分钟!</font>
Five minutes, please.

1015
01:42:49,240 --> 01:42:50,620
<font size=24>休息五分钟!</font>
Five minutes!

1016
01:42:52,240 --> 01:42:53,490
<font size=24>什么事?</font>
Yes?

1017
01:42:53,700 --> 01:42:59,420
<font size=24>你不知道陛下禁止在歌剧中表演芭雷舞吗?</font>
Do you not know that His Majesty has expressly forbidden ballet in operas?

1018
01:42:59,670 --> 01:43:04,590
<font size=24>-这不是芭雷舞  这是婚礼舞蹈!  -没错  舞蹈</font>
-It's not a ballet, it's a dance. -Exactly. A dance.

1019
01:43:04,760 --> 01:43:09,430
<font size=24>陛下当然不是禁止故事中有跳舞</font>
Surely, His Majesty didn't mean no dancing when it's in the story.

1020
01:43:09,680 --> 01:43:15,140
<font size=24>任意解释陛下的意旨是很危险的  把乐谱给我</font>
It's dangerous to interpret his edicts. Give me your score, please.

1021
01:43:24,030 --> 01:43:25,740
<font size=24>谢谢!</font>
Thank you.

1022
01:43:28,910 --> 01:43:31,910
<font size=24>院长先生  你干什么?  你在干什么?</font>
What are you doing, Herr Direktor?

1023
01:43:32,120 --> 01:43:35,750
<font size=24>除去不适合的部分</font>
Taking out what you should never have put in.

1024
01:43:36,870 --> 01:43:39,580
<font size=24>求求你</font>
Please. Please!

1025
01:43:39,960 --> 01:43:42,420
<font size=24>我没有别人可求了</font>
I have no one else to turn to.

1026
01:43:42,630 --> 01:43:45,300
<font size=24>-莫扎特  什么事?  -你不会相信的!</font>
-What is it? -It's unbelievable.

1027
01:43:45,460 --> 01:43:49,680
<font size=24>院长将我歌剧的大部份都去除</font>
The direktor has torn up a huge section of my music.

1028
01:43:49,890 --> 01:43:53,100
<font size=24>他们说我应该重写</font>
They say I have to rewrite the opera.

1029
01:43:53,720 --> 01:43:56,220
<font size=24>但这作品已经很完美了</font>
But it's perfect as it is.

1030
01:43:56,430 --> 01:43:57,680
<font size=24>我不能...</font>
I can't...

1031
01:43:57,890 --> 01:44:00,480
<font size=24>改写已经是完美的作品</font>
rewrite what's perfect.

1032
01:44:02,270 --> 01:44:03,650
<font size=24>求您</font>
Please.

1033
01:44:03,820 --> 01:44:06,230
<font size=24>你不能去找他说些好话好吗?</font>
Can't you talk to him?

1034
01:44:06,740 --> 01:44:07,990
<font size=24>求您</font>
Please.

1035
01:44:08,200 --> 01:44:10,990
<font size=24>我都很讨厌他了  何况是你</font>
Why bother? He's no friend of yours.

1036
01:44:11,200 --> 01:44:14,910
<font size=24>我真的想杀了他</font>
I could kill him! I mean, really! Kill him!

1037
01:44:16,910 --> 01:44:21,000
<font size=24>我气的将乐谱丢到火炉中</font>
I threw the entire score into the fire, he made me so angry.

1038
01:44:21,250 --> 01:44:26,500
<font size=24>-你把乐谱给烧了?  -没有  我太太及时救回来了</font>
-You burned the score? -No, my wife took it out in time.

1039
01:44:28,130 --> 01:44:29,510
<font size=24>谢天谢地</font>
Thank God.

1040
01:44:31,220 --> 01:44:36,260
<font size=24>这种人可以审核我们的作品真是不公平</font>
It's unfair that a man like that should have power over our work!

1041
01:44:37,600 --> 01:44:40,980
<font size=24>但有人却可以控制他</font>
But there are those who have power over him.

1042
01:44:42,650 --> 01:44:46,020
<font size=24>我直接跟陛下谈</font>
I think I'll take this up with the emperor.

1043
01:44:47,940 --> 01:44:49,440
<font size=24>太好了</font>
Excellency...

1044
01:44:49,650 --> 01:44:50,860
<font size=24>真的吗?</font>
would you?

1045
01:44:52,530 --> 01:44:55,450
<font size=24>我全心全意的去做  莫扎特</font>
With all my heart, Mozart.

1046
01:44:56,540 --> 01:44:59,040
<font size=24>谢谢你</font>
Thank you.

1047
01:44:59,250 --> 01:45:04,210
<font size=24>好了!  好了!  我又不是教宗</font>
Please, Herr Mozart. "Please, it's not a holy relic."

1048
01:45:06,380 --> 01:45:11,170
<font size=24>当然我什么也没告诉陛下</font>
I don't need to tell you I said nothing, whatever, to the emperor.

1049
01:45:11,380 --> 01:45:16,050
<font size=24>我照常去剧场骗骗莫扎特</font>
I went to the theater to tell Mozart something, anything...

1050
01:45:17,560 --> 01:45:22,310
<font size=24>突然在第三幕当中</font>
when suddenly, in the middle of the third act...

1051
01:45:22,520 --> 01:45:30,480
<font size=24>从不参观排演的陛下竟然来了</font>
to my astonishment, the emperor...who never attended rehearsals, suddenly appeared.

1052
01:45:49,170 --> 01:45:51,300
<font size=24>这在干什么?</font>
What is this?

1053
01:45:53,760 --> 01:45:55,720
<font size=24>我不了解</font>
I don't understand.

1054
01:45:56,760 --> 01:45:58,180
<font size=24>这就是最前卫的吗?</font>
Is it modern?

1055
01:45:59,220 --> 01:46:00,930
<font size=24>陛下...</font>
Majesty...

1056
01:46:01,180 --> 01:46:02,890
<font size=24>院长将...</font>
the Herr Direktor...

1057
01:46:03,100 --> 01:46:10,690
<font size=24>芭雷舞部分的乐曲...除去了</font>
he has removed un balletto...that would have occurred at this place.

1058
01:46:11,690 --> 01:46:13,110
<font size=24>为什么?</font>
Why?

1059
01:46:13,450 --> 01:46:15,610
<font size=24>这是你的规定</font>
It is your regulation, sire.

1060
01:46:15,820 --> 01:46:18,870
<font size=24>歌剧院里不准上演芭蕾舞</font>
No ballet in your opera.

1061
01:46:24,620 --> 01:46:26,370
<font size=24>萨列里</font>
Salieri.

1062
01:46:27,750 --> 01:46:29,460
<font size=24>你喜欢这样子吗?</font>
Do you like this?

1063
01:46:31,880 --> 01:46:35,630
<font size=24>这不是喜不喜欢的问题</font>
It's not a question of liking, Majesty.

1064
01:46:35,880 --> 01:46:38,930
<font size=24>你的法律这样规定的</font>
Your own law decrees it, I'm afraid.

1065
01:46:40,640 --> 01:46:42,930
<font size=24>看看他们</font>
Well, look at them!

1066
01:46:45,060 --> 01:46:48,270
<font size=24>不...这简直是乱来</font>
No! This is nonsense!

1067
01:46:48,480 --> 01:46:52,480
<font size=24>-配上音乐再让我看看  -可是  陛下</font>
-Let me see the scene with the music. -But, sire!

1068
01:46:52,730 --> 01:46:54,150
<font size=24>这是命令!</font>
Oblige me!

1069
01:46:54,400 --> 01:46:56,450
<font size=24>是的  陛下</font>
Yes, Majesty.

1070
01:47:05,500 --> 01:47:08,790
<font size=24>可不可以配上音乐再给我们看一次</font>
Can we see the scene with the music, please?

1071
01:47:09,000 --> 01:47:12,340
<font size=24>当然可以!  院长先生</font>
Certainly! Certainly, Herr Direktor!

1072
01:47:17,930 --> 01:47:20,680
<font size=24>将宫庭那一景弄回来</font>
Bring the palace set back in, please.

1073
01:47:58,720 --> 01:48:03,050
<font size=24>还原后的第三幕大胆绝妙</font>
The restored third act...was bold, brilliant.

1074
01:48:03,930 --> 01:48:05,930
<font size=24>第四幕...</font>
The fourth...

1075
01:48:08,390 --> 01:48:10,350
<font size=24>真是美得不可思议</font>
was astounding.

1076
01:48:18,400 --> 01:48:19,860
<font size=24>一位女士...</font>
I saw a woman...

1077
01:48:20,070 --> 01:48:25,870
<font size=24>伪装成一位女佣  他先生向她倾诉...</font>
disguised in her maid's clothes hear her husband speak the first...

1078
01:48:26,080 --> 01:48:29,500
<font size=24>多年未说的情话</font>
tender words he has offered her in years.

1079
01:48:29,710 --> 01:48:34,420
<font size=24>只因为他以为她是别人</font>
Simply because he thinks she is someone else.

1080
01:48:35,090 --> 01:48:40,550
<font size=24>我听到充满宽恕的音符散在剧场</font>
I heard the music of true forgiveness filling the theater...

1081
01:48:40,760 --> 01:48:45,260
<font size=24>全场听众全部沉醉在那音乐中</font>
conferring on all who sat there, perfect absolution.

1082
01:48:46,010 --> 01:48:49,180
<font size=24>上帝又因莫扎特...</font>
God was singing through this little man...

1083
01:48:49,390 --> 01:48:51,940
<font size=24>而呈现给世上</font>
to all the world.

1084
01:48:52,560 --> 01:48:54,520
<font size=24>从不停止的</font>
Unstoppable.

1085
01:48:54,730 --> 01:49:00,110
<font size=24>每一小节都会我觉得失败得更深</font>
Making my defeat more bitter with every passing bar.

1086
01:49:38,320 --> 01:49:41,110
<font size=24>然后  你知道发生了什么事</font>
And then, do you know what happened?

1087
01:49:44,280 --> 01:49:45,820
<font size=24>奇迹</font>
A miracle!

1088
01:49:52,960 --> 01:49:54,330
<font size=24>因为那哈欠</font>
With that yawn...

1089
01:49:54,750 --> 01:49:58,670
<font size=24>我的失败转为成功</font>
I saw my defeat turn into a victory.

1090
01:50:02,510 --> 01:50:06,300
<font size=24>他还算运气只让陛下打一次哈欠</font>
Mozart was lucky the emperor yawned only once.

1091
01:50:06,510 --> 01:50:07,970
<font size=24>如果有三次</font>
Three yawns...

1092
01:50:08,180 --> 01:50:11,180
<font size=24>当晚就会停演</font>
and the opera would fail the same night.

1093
01:50:11,430 --> 01:50:14,770
<font size=24>两次次的话  最多演一星期</font>
Two yawns, within a week at most.

1094
01:50:14,980 --> 01:50:19,940
<font size=24>一次的话  作曲家仍然可以</font>
With one yawn, the composer could still get....

1095
01:50:21,650 --> 01:50:26,450
<font size=24>九场!  就只有九场现在就被取消了?</font>
Nine performances! Nine! That's all it's had! Withdrawn!

1096
01:50:26,660 --> 01:50:28,950
<font size=24>我知道!</font>
I know, I know.

1097
01:50:29,200 --> 01:50:30,950
<font size=24>真是太令人气愤了</font>
It's outrageous.

1098
01:50:32,580 --> 01:50:36,330
<font size=24>不过大家要是不喜欢的作品</font>
Still, if the public doesn't like one's work...

1099
01:50:36,670 --> 01:50:39,210
<font size=24>我们还是要接受这事实</font>
one has to accept the fact gracefully.

1100
01:50:39,380 --> 01:50:42,460
<font size=24>但他们为什么不喜欢!</font>
But what is it that they don't like?

1101
01:50:43,010 --> 01:50:45,380
<font size=24>我知道陛下为什么不喜欢</font>
I can speak for the emperor.

1102
01:50:45,590 --> 01:50:48,800
<font size=24>因为太长了</font>
You make too many demands on the royal ear.

1103
01:50:49,010 --> 01:50:54,350
<font size=24>他只能集中精神的听上一小时  你却要演上个四小时</font>
The poor man can't concentrate for more than an hour. You gave him four.

1104
01:50:59,650 --> 01:51:02,480
<font size=24>你认为怎样?</font>
What did you think of it yourself?

1105
01:51:02,690 --> 01:51:05,190
<font size=24>你喜欢吗?</font>
Did you like it at all?

1106
01:51:06,740 --> 01:51:09,370
<font size=24>很美妙!</font>
I thought it was marvelous.

1107
01:51:09,620 --> 01:51:13,240
<font size=24>当然了  这是前无古人之作</font>
Of course. It's the best opera yet written.

1108
01:51:13,580 --> 01:51:15,160
<font size=24>我知道</font>
I know it!

1109
01:51:18,040 --> 01:51:19,750
<font size=24>他们为什么不来?</font>
Why didn't they come?

1110
01:51:22,630 --> 01:51:26,340
<font size=24>你高估了维也纳人的水准</font>
I think you overestimate our dear Viennese, friend.

1111
01:51:26,550 --> 01:51:30,050
<font size=24>你甚至没有在歌曲结尾时</font>
You didn't give them a bang at the end of songs...

1112
01:51:30,260 --> 01:51:32,720
<font size=24>给他们一些鼓掌的暗示</font>
to let them know when to clap.

1113
01:51:33,430 --> 01:51:35,930
<font size=24>我明白了</font>
I know, I know.

1114
01:51:36,140 --> 01:51:39,600
<font size=24>也许你该在这方面教我一些</font>
Maybe you should give me some lessons in that.

1115
01:51:40,650 --> 01:51:43,150
<font size=24>我不会那么冒昧</font>
I wouldn't presume.

1116
01:51:46,280 --> 01:51:49,280
<font size=24>虽然我知道有点冒犯...</font>
Nevertheless, at the risk of imposing...

1117
01:51:49,530 --> 01:51:52,530
<font size=24>我想请你看我的新作品</font>
I'd like you to see my new piece.

1118
01:51:53,790 --> 01:51:55,950
<font size=24>那是我莫大的荣幸</font>
It would be an honor for me.

1119
01:51:56,200 --> 01:51:58,870
<font size=24>不  这才是我的荣耀</font>
No, the honor would be all mine.

1120
01:53:25,040 --> 01:53:29,880
<font size=24>我相信</font>
I believe....I believe...

1121
01:53:30,050 --> 01:53:34,050
<font size=24>这是有始以来最好的歌剧作品</font>
it is the best opera yet written, my friends.

1122
01:53:36,140 --> 01:53:37,760
<font size=24>萨列里</font>
Salieri!

1123
01:53:39,180 --> 01:53:43,230
<font size=24>你是音乐界最好的作曲家</font>
You are the brightest star in the musical firmament.

1124
01:53:43,390 --> 01:53:46,900
<font size=24>维也纳与我向你致敬</font>
You do honor to Vienna and to me.

1125
01:54:13,550 --> 01:54:14,930
<font size=24>莫扎特!</font>
Herr Mozart!

1126
01:54:15,800 --> 01:54:19,010
<font size=24>-你来了我很高兴  -我怎么可能不来</font>
-It was good of you to come. -How could I not?

1127
01:54:22,350 --> 01:54:25,190
<font size=24>你喜欢我的作品吗?</font>
Did my work please you?

1128
01:54:26,600 --> 01:54:30,570
<font size=24>我从不知道有人能写出这种音乐</font>
I never knew that music like that was possible.

1129
01:54:31,780 --> 01:54:34,440
<font size=24>-你只是在恭维我  -不  是真的</font>
-You flatter me. -No, no.

1130
01:54:35,410 --> 01:54:37,780
<font size=24>当人们听到这音乐</font>
One hears such sounds...

1131
01:54:37,950 --> 01:54:41,410
<font size=24>就会想到  萨列里</font>
and what can one say but: Salieri!

1132
01:54:48,790 --> 01:54:54,380
<font size=24>每人在这里  我们来客人了  我们有酒!</font>
Everybody's here, and we've got guests. Bravo! I've got some more.

1133
01:54:54,590 --> 01:54:58,340
<font size=24>你记得我的好朋友希克</font>
You remember my good friend Schikaneder. Come in.

1134
01:54:58,550 --> 01:54:59,850
<font size=24>进来别害差</font>
Don't be shy.

1135
01:55:00,050 --> 01:55:04,270
<font size=24>这位是个好女孩  这位也是</font>
-This is a very nice girl, and this -Wolfie?

1136
01:55:05,270 --> 01:55:07,310
<font size=24>怎么了  亲爱的</font>
Yes, my love?

1137
01:55:07,770 --> 01:55:11,360
<font size=24>波非  这而位是从沙德堡来的</font>
-These gentlemen are from Salzburg. -Salzburg?

1138
01:55:12,610 --> 01:55:14,480
<font size=24>沙德堡!  我们正在说沙德堡!</font>
We were just talking about Salzburg.

1139
01:55:14,650 --> 01:55:16,110
<font size=24>波非</font>
Wolfie....

1140
01:55:17,780 --> 01:55:20,280
<font size=24>你父亲去逝了</font>
Your father is dead.

1141
01:55:42,680 --> 01:55:45,310
<font size=24>可怕的鬼魂...</font>
So rose the dreadful ghost...

1142
01:55:45,520 --> 01:55:49,900
<font size=24>出现在他下个作品</font>
from his next and blackest opera.

1143
01:55:55,190 --> 01:55:59,530
<font size=24>舞台上站着的是死去的指挥官</font>
There on the stage, stood the figure of a dead commander.

1144
01:55:59,780 --> 01:56:01,370
<font size=24>我知道...</font>
I knew...

1145
01:56:01,530 --> 01:56:03,330
<font size=24>只有我了解...</font>
only I understood...

1146
01:56:03,530 --> 01:56:08,710
<font size=24>那是他父亲的替身</font>
that the horrifying apparition was Leopold...raised from the dead!

1147
01:56:38,320 --> 01:56:42,320
<font size=24>莫扎特其实是在召唤他的亲身父亲</font>
Wolfgang had actually summoned up his own father...

1148
01:56:42,530 --> 01:56:46,240
<font size=24>在全世界面前表达一个做儿子的孝心!</font>
to accuse his son before all the world!

1149
01:56:47,580 --> 01:56:49,450
<font size=24>看的</font>
It was...

1150
01:56:49,660 --> 01:56:53,080
<font size=24>真是恐怖而美妙</font>
terrifying and wonderful to watch.

1151
01:57:57,150 --> 01:57:58,650
<font size=24>于是...</font>
And now...

1152
01:58:04,160 --> 01:58:07,280
<font size=24>疯狂就在我心中产生了</font>
the madness began in me.

1153
01:58:09,540 --> 01:58:13,080
<font size=24>精神一分为二</font>
The madness of a man splitting in half.

1154
01:58:16,580 --> 01:58:19,290
<font size=24>因为我的影响</font>
Through my influence, I saw to it...

1155
01:58:19,500 --> 01:58:23,340
<font size=24>《唐乔望尼》只演了五场</font>
Don Giovanni was played only five times in Vienna.

1156
01:58:23,590 --> 01:58:28,180
<font size=24>但我五场却都去了</font>
But, in secret, I went to every one of those five.

1157
01:58:28,430 --> 01:58:33,350
<font size=24>以祟敬的心欣赏似乎只有我一人</font>
Worshiping sound I alone seemed to hear.

1158
01:59:20,020 --> 01:59:23,480
<font size=24>在听他的音乐  在那儿我了解到</font>
And as I stood there, understanding how...

1159
01:59:23,690 --> 01:59:27,240
<font size=24>他生气的父亲  虽然死了</font>
that bitter old man was still possessing his poor son...

1160
01:59:27,490 --> 01:59:30,160
<font size=24>可是仍然支配着他</font>
even from beyond the grave...

1161
01:59:30,410 --> 01:59:32,240
<font size=24>我开始有了计划</font>
I began to see a way...

1162
01:59:32,540 --> 01:59:34,330
<font size=24>一个可怕的计划</font>
a terrible way...

1163
01:59:34,540 --> 01:59:39,500
<font size=24>可以胜过上帝的计划!</font>
I could finally triumph...over God.

1164
02:02:49,570 --> 02:02:51,270
<font size=24>莫扎特?</font>
Herr Mozart?

1165
02:02:54,240 --> 02:02:57,360
<font size=24>我要请你作曲</font>
I have come to commission work from you.

1166
02:02:58,740 --> 02:03:03,120
<font size=24>什么曲子?</font>
-What work? -A Mass for the dead.

1167
02:03:03,330 --> 02:03:05,290
<font size=24>安魂曲!</font>
What dead?

1168
02:03:05,710 --> 02:03:07,790
<font size=24>谁死了?</font>
Who is dead?

1169
02:03:07,960 --> 02:03:12,630
<font size=24>一位应享有安魂曲而没得到的人</font>
A man who deserved a Requiem Mass and never got one.

1170
02:03:12,880 --> 02:03:16,420
<font size=24>-你是谁?  -我只是个信差</font>
-Who are you? -I am only a messenger.

1171
02:03:16,630 --> 02:03:18,840
<font size=24>你接受吗?</font>
Do you accept?

1172
02:03:19,140 --> 02:03:21,550
<font size=24>报酬很好</font>
You will be well paid.

1173
02:03:29,110 --> 02:03:31,360
<font size=24>你接受吗?</font>
Do you accept?

1174
02:03:41,950 --> 02:03:43,410
<font size=24>尽快完成</font>
Work fast.

1175
02:03:43,620 --> 02:03:46,370
<font size=24>不要对别人提起这事</font>
And be sure tell no one what you do.

1176
02:03:46,580 --> 02:03:49,080
<font size=24>我会很快的再来看你</font>
You will see me again soon.

1177
02:04:38,170 --> 02:04:41,010
<font size=24>我的计划很简单</font>
My plan was so simple...

1178
02:04:42,050 --> 02:04:44,550
<font size=24>但却很吓人</font>
that it terrified me.

1179
02:04:46,640 --> 02:04:50,560
<font size=24>首先我要拿到安魂曲  然后</font>
First, I must get the death Mass, and then...

1180
02:04:52,560 --> 02:04:55,570
<font size=24>再完成莫扎特的死亡</font>
I must achieve his death.

1181
02:04:57,070 --> 02:04:58,740
<font size=24>什么?</font>
What?

1182
02:04:59,570 --> 02:05:01,700
<font size=24>他的葬礼!</font>
His funeral!

1183
02:05:02,530 --> 02:05:03,820
<font size=24>想像一下</font>
Imagine it!

1184
02:05:04,030 --> 02:05:07,080
<font size=24>在教堂  所有的维也纳人都在那里</font>
The cathedral, all Vienna sitting there.

1185
02:05:07,370 --> 02:05:12,710
<font size=24>莫扎特小小的棺材躺在维也纳的中央</font>
His coffin. Mozart's little coffin in the middle.

1186
02:05:13,380 --> 02:05:15,080
<font size=24>然后</font>
And then...

1187
02:05:15,750 --> 02:05:18,000
<font size=24>一片沉寂中</font>
in that silence...

1188
02:05:20,170 --> 02:05:22,090
<font size=24>音乐扬起</font>
music.

1189
02:05:23,430 --> 02:05:25,720
<font size=24>神圣的音乐</font>
A divine music...

1190
02:05:25,930 --> 02:05:28,850
<font size=24>超脱所有的一切</font>
bursts out over them all.

1191
02:05:29,480 --> 02:05:33,190
<font size=24>伟大的死亡</font>
A great Mass of death.

1192
02:05:34,480 --> 02:05:38,440
<font size=24>伟大的为莫扎特而作的安魂曲</font>
Requiem Mass for Wolfgang Mozart.

1193
02:05:38,610 --> 02:05:42,900
<font size=24>由他生前最好的朋友...</font>
Composed by his devoted friend...

1194
02:05:43,280 --> 02:05:46,070
<font size=24>萨列里写的</font>
Antonio Salieri.

1195
02:05:47,030 --> 02:05:48,740
<font size=24>在音乐中那么庄严</font>
What sublimity!

1196
02:05:48,950 --> 02:05:51,540
<font size=24>那么气派</font>
What depth!

1197
02:05:51,750 --> 02:05:54,790
<font size=24>那么热情</font>
What passion in the music!

1198
02:05:55,540 --> 02:05:59,460
<font size=24>萨列里终于受到神的付托</font>
Salieri has been touched by God at last...

1199
02:05:59,630 --> 02:06:02,300
<font size=24>上帝也被迫要听萨列里的</font>
and God forced to listen!

1200
02:06:03,760 --> 02:06:07,300
<font size=24>也无法阻止萨列里</font>
Powerless to stop it!

1201
02:06:07,510 --> 02:06:10,970
<font size=24>我终于也反过来笑他了</font>
I, for once, in the end, laughing at him!

1202
02:06:18,400 --> 02:06:22,650
<font size=24>使我担心的  是如何实际杀人</font>
The only thing that worried me was the actual killing.

1203
02:06:22,900 --> 02:06:25,280
<font size=24>我怎么作的呢?</font>
How does one do that?

1204
02:06:26,030 --> 02:06:28,830
<font size=24>人们如何能杀人呢?</font>
How does one kill a man?

1205
02:06:30,040 --> 02:06:32,040
<font size=24>梦想...</font>
It's one thing...

1206
02:06:32,250 --> 02:06:34,620
<font size=24>是一回事</font>
to dream about it.

1207
02:06:34,830 --> 02:06:38,080
<font size=24>实际作的时候...</font>
Very different when you....

1208
02:06:40,420 --> 02:06:42,800
<font size=24>非常不一样了</font>
When you have to do it...

1209
02:06:45,340 --> 02:06:47,800
<font size=24>用自己的一双手</font>
with your own hands.

1210
02:06:57,310 --> 02:07:00,110
<font size=24>请进</font>
Come in!

1211
02:07:15,660 --> 02:07:20,210
<font size=24>我来吃晚餐</font>
I've come to dinner

1212
02:07:20,420 --> 02:07:23,210
<font size=24>晚餐?  你疯了是不是  我是贵族</font>
Dinner! Are you mad? I'm a nobleman!

1213
02:07:23,420 --> 02:07:26,880
<font size=24>我只和与我同高的人吃饭</font>
I only ever dine with people of my own height!

1214
02:07:27,130 --> 02:07:28,890
<font size=24>停下</font>
Stop it!

1215
02:07:29,550 --> 02:07:31,680
<font size=24>当心  当心</font>
Be careful Be careful

1216
02:07:31,890 --> 02:07:34,770
<font size=24>抓紧</font>
Hold tight

1217
02:07:35,270 --> 02:07:37,560
<font size=24>我是著名的...</font>
I'm a famous...

1218
02:07:37,730 --> 02:07:40,560
<font size=24>骑手</font>
horseman

1219
02:07:40,730 --> 02:07:45,070
<font size=24>我们是有名的马</font>
And we're a famous horsy

1220
02:07:47,070 --> 02:07:51,070
<font size=24>踢我一脚  亲爱的</font>
Give me a hoof, my darling

1221
02:07:51,240 --> 02:07:56,410
<font size=24>而我会给你我的心</font>
And I'll give you my heart

1222
02:07:56,660 --> 02:08:01,170
<font size=24>把我带到你的马厩</font>
Take me to your stable

1223
02:08:01,380 --> 02:08:04,670
<font size=24>我们永远也不会分开</font>
And nevermore we'll part

1224
02:08:11,760 --> 02:08:14,760
<font size=24>杀了我  杀了我</font>
Kill me Kill me

1225
02:08:36,120 --> 02:08:40,960
<font size=24>我们将进入女高音的部分</font>
We're going to make a soprano stew

1226
02:08:41,130 --> 02:08:45,800
<font size=24>我们将进入女高音的部分</font>
We're going to make a soprano stew

1227
02:08:46,000 --> 02:08:49,800
<font size=24>我们将进入女高音的部分</font>
And when you make a soprano stew

1228
02:08:49,970 --> 02:08:51,840
<font size=24>闭嘴!</font>
Shut up!

1229
02:08:52,090 --> 02:08:54,800
<font size=24>那样的曲调会让我死亡</font>
I'm sick to death of that tune!

1230
02:09:13,740 --> 02:09:17,330
<font size=24>给我一些干草  我的亲爱的</font>
Give me some hay, my darling

1231
02:09:17,540 --> 02:09:21,120
<font size=24>而我将给你我的心</font>
And I'll give you my heart

1232
02:09:21,330 --> 02:09:23,500
<font size=24>干草!  干草!</font>
Leporello! Some hay!

1233
02:10:14,380 --> 02:10:16,510
<font size=24>我希望...</font>
We hope...

1234
02:10:16,720 --> 02:10:20,890
<font size=24>你能得到满足</font>
you're contented

1235
02:10:22,180 --> 02:10:24,810
<font size=24>伴随着...</font>
With what...

1236
02:10:25,020 --> 02:10:29,190
<font size=24>我们的演出</font>
we've presented

1237
02:10:30,030 --> 02:10:36,700
<font size=24>喜欢我们的和平鸽</font>
And love our dove of peace

1238
02:10:37,120 --> 02:10:43,870
<font size=24>喜欢...</font>
And love...

1239
02:10:44,080 --> 02:10:48,080
<font size=24>我们的和平鸽</font>
our dove of peace

1240
02:11:01,890 --> 02:11:04,600
<font size=24>-你觉得如何?  -好极了</font>
-What did you think? -It was wonderful!

1241
02:11:04,850 --> 02:11:09,060
<font size=24>-他喜欢那些朱儒  -很有趣</font>
-He liked the little people. -It's all in good fun.

1242
02:11:10,230 --> 02:11:12,440
<font size=24>我喜欢马</font>
I liked the horse.

1243
02:11:23,410 --> 02:11:27,000
<font size=24>如果你在这里演《唐乔望尼》</font>
I tell you, if you played Don Giovanni here...

1244
02:11:27,460 --> 02:11:30,460
<font size=24>你必会大获成功</font>
you would've had a wonderful success.

1245
02:11:30,630 --> 02:11:32,420
<font size=24>你属于这里</font>
You belong here.

1246
02:11:32,630 --> 02:11:36,800
<font size=24>不是属于虚伪的宫廷  你可以做你想做的任何事</font>
Not at the snobby court. You could do anything you like.

1247
02:11:37,010 --> 02:11:41,800
<font size=24>愈荒唐愈好  那才是人们要的  想像力</font>
The more fantastic, the better. That's what people want: fantasy.

1248
02:11:42,010 --> 02:11:45,270
<font size=24>你应替我写个适当的角巴</font>
You write a proper part for me...

1249
02:11:45,480 --> 02:11:47,770
<font size=24>几首感人的歌</font>
a couple of catchy songs...

1250
02:11:47,980 --> 02:11:52,320
<font size=24>我保证你一定成功</font>
I guarantee you a triumph deluxe!

1251
02:11:52,980 --> 02:11:57,110
<font size=24>-你怎么认为?  -你要付我们多少钱</font>
-What do you say? -How much will you pay him?

1252
02:11:57,320 --> 02:11:58,820
<font size=24>啊!</font>
Ah!

1253
02:11:58,990 --> 02:12:02,620
<font size=24>你带着你的经纪人</font>
Well! I see you brought your manager with you.

1254
02:12:04,490 --> 02:12:06,620
<font size=24>太太</font>
Well, madame...

1255
02:12:06,830 --> 02:12:10,000
<font size=24>全部收入的一半如何</font>
how about half the receipts?

1256
02:12:10,420 --> 02:12:12,000
<font size=24>收入的一半!</font>
Half the receipts!

1257
02:12:12,170 --> 02:12:14,500
<font size=24>太太!  我是指现付!</font>
-Stanzi! -I'm talking about now.

1258
02:12:14,710 --> 02:12:18,170
<font size=24>要现付多少定金</font>
How much will you pay him now? Down payment.

1259
02:12:18,430 --> 02:12:20,430
<font size=24>定金!</font>
Down payment?

1260
02:12:21,510 --> 02:12:25,010
<font size=24>你以为我是谁?  皇帝?</font>
Who do you think I am, the emperor?

1261
02:12:25,220 --> 02:12:27,520
<font size=24>我该走了</font>
Whoops. I have to go.

1262
02:12:27,730 --> 02:12:30,850
<font size=24>好好欣赏下一段</font>
Stay here, you'll enjoy this next one.

1263
02:12:32,440 --> 02:12:33,810
<font size=24>你不会接受吧!</font>
You won't do this.

1264
02:12:34,020 --> 02:12:36,360
<font size=24>-为什么不  全部收入的一半  -什么时候?</font>
-Why not? Half the house! -When?

1265
02:12:36,570 --> 02:12:40,660
<font size=24>我们现在就需要钱  不是付定金就是不作</font>
We need money now! He pays you now, or you don't do it.

1266
02:12:40,860 --> 02:12:42,490
<font size=24>我不信任他</font>
I don't trust that man.

1267
02:12:42,700 --> 02:12:46,330
<font size=24>也不喜欢他处理你歌剧的方式太通俗</font>
I don't like what he did with your opera. It was common.

1268
02:12:46,540 --> 02:12:49,540
<font size=24>不过你喜欢吧  小伙子</font>
You liked it. Monkey, punky, flunky!

1269
02:12:49,710 --> 02:12:51,250
<font size=24>收入的一半!</font>
Half the house.

1270
02:12:51,500 --> 02:12:55,540
<font size=24>你一毛也拿不到!  我要现在拿到手!</font>
You'll never see a penny. I want it here in my hand.

1271
02:12:55,750 --> 02:12:59,470
<font size=24>-好呀!  在这儿  -闭嘴</font>
-I'll put it here in your hand. -Shut up!

1272
02:12:59,680 --> 02:13:03,590
<font size=24>没有钱休想碰我</font>
You won't put a thing in my hand until I see some money!

1273
02:13:04,890 --> 02:13:09,480
<font size=24>真是令人为难  你能想像有谁能为他做事吗?</font>
It's embarrassing. Can't you think of anyone who can do something for him?

1274
02:13:10,100 --> 02:13:14,060
<font size=24>我想莫扎特可能是最后一个</font>
I'm afraid Mozart is a lost cause, baron.

1275
02:13:14,610 --> 02:13:18,900
<font size=24>他在维也纳取得了巨大成功</font>
He has succeeded in alienating practically the whole of Vienna.

1276
02:13:19,070 --> 02:13:20,990
<font size=24>他从未还钱</font>
He never pays his debts.

1277
02:13:21,200 --> 02:13:25,240
<font size=24>我想像不出我能把他推荐给谁</font>
I can't think of anyone to whom I'd dare recommend him.

1278
02:13:25,410 --> 02:13:29,700
<font size=24>莫扎特  真是奇怪!</font>
Herr Mozart. What a surprise!

1279
02:13:30,790 --> 02:13:33,080
<font size=24>有什么能帮你吗?</font>
What can I do for you?

1280
02:13:34,420 --> 02:13:38,920
<font size=24>我的学生对学习音乐依然感兴趣吗?</font>
Is my pupil still interested in learning the art of music?

1281
02:13:40,510 --> 02:13:45,300
<font size=24>你的学生已经结婚住在很远的地方  年轻人</font>
Your pupil is married and living in Mannheim, young man.

1282
02:13:45,930 --> 02:13:47,600
<font size=24>真的吗?</font>
Really?

1283
02:13:53,100 --> 02:13:58,770
<font size=24>或许你的亲爱的老婆想学习呢?</font>
Perhaps your dear wife might care to profit from my instruction.

1284
02:13:59,230 --> 02:14:01,530
<font size=24>怎么了?  莫扎特?</font>
What is it, Mozart?

1285
02:14:01,740 --> 02:14:04,410
<font size=24>你怎么了?</font>
What's the matter with you?

1286
02:14:04,610 --> 02:14:11,160
<font size=24>既然这表明没人想请我</font>
Well ...since it appears no one is eager to hire my services...

1287
02:14:11,410 --> 02:14:15,120
<font size=24>您能帮忙借点钱给我吗?</font>
could you favor me with a little money instead?

1288
02:14:18,170 --> 02:14:19,630
<font size=24>用来做什么用?</font>
What for?

1289
02:14:21,170 --> 02:14:25,340
<font size=24>一个男人赚不到钱  就得去向别人借</font>
If a man cannot earn, he must borrow.

1290
02:14:28,760 --> 02:14:31,810
<font size=24>那样很难</font>
That's hardly the way to go about it.

1291
02:14:32,770 --> 02:14:36,150
<font size=24>你说得对</font>
You are right, sir. You are right.

1292
02:14:36,310 --> 02:14:40,820
<font size=24>你也知道  我才华洋溢  你很富有</font>
But you see, I am endowed with talent, and you with money.

1293
02:14:40,980 --> 02:14:42,940
<font size=24>如果我给我的...</font>
If I offer mine...

1294
02:14:43,150 --> 02:14:45,820
<font size=24>你就得把你的给我</font>
you should offer yours.

1295
02:14:48,990 --> 02:14:51,160
<font size=24>对不起  不行</font>
I'm sorry, no.

1296
02:14:53,960 --> 02:14:55,620
<font size=24>求求你</font>
Please.

1297
02:14:57,500 --> 02:15:00,090
<font size=24>我的回答是不  莫扎特</font>
My answer is no, Mozart.

1298
02:15:06,300 --> 02:15:08,180
<font size=24>拜托!  拜托!</font>
Please.

1299
02:15:12,390 --> 02:15:14,600
<font size=24>莫扎特!  莫扎特!</font>
Please!

1300
02:15:51,430 --> 02:15:53,560
<font size=24>别理他</font>
Don't answer it.

1301
02:15:55,430 --> 02:15:57,140
<font size=24>为何?</font>
Why?

1302
02:15:59,350 --> 02:16:01,060
<font size=24>告诉他...</font>
Tell him....

1303
02:16:02,190 --> 02:16:04,400
<font size=24>告诉他我不在</font>
Tell him I'm not here.

1304
02:16:04,780 --> 02:16:06,740
<font size=24>告诉他...</font>
Tell him....

1305
02:16:07,740 --> 02:16:10,240
<font size=24>说我正在工作</font>
Tell him I'm working on it.

1306
02:16:11,240 --> 02:16:13,410
<font size=24>稍后回来</font>
Come back later.

1307
02:16:29,550 --> 02:16:32,470
<font size=24>-抱歉  打扰你了吗?  -不</font>
Am I interrupting?  No.

1308
02:16:32,760 --> 02:16:35,600
<font size=24>我的朋友呢?</font>
Good. Where's our friend?

1309
02:16:35,770 --> 02:16:37,770
<font size=24>不在这里</font>
He's not here.

1310
02:16:38,270 --> 02:16:41,770
<font size=24>他说他正在继续作曲中</font>
But he's working on it, he told me to tell you.

1311
02:16:42,730 --> 02:16:44,690
<font size=24>那些吗?</font>
Is that it?

1312
02:16:50,490 --> 02:16:52,990
<font size=24>他满意吗?</font>
Is he happy with it?

1313
02:16:55,990 --> 02:16:59,000
<font size=24>这是什么?  安魂曲</font>
What's this? A Requiem Mass?

1314
02:16:59,250 --> 02:17:03,460
<font size=24>-认为我是在参加葬礼  -放下</font>
-You think I'm in the funeral business? -Leave that alone!

1315
02:17:03,630 --> 02:17:08,010
<font size=24>-放下  那不是给你的  -对不起</font>
-Put it down! It's not for you! -I'm sorry.

1316
02:17:08,420 --> 02:17:10,420
<font size=24>我要你替我作的曲你写了没有</font>
What have you got for me?

1317
02:17:11,430 --> 02:17:13,010
<font size=24>完成了吗?</font>
Finished?

1318
02:17:14,430 --> 02:17:19,100
<font size=24>-什么?  -The vaudeville  你认为是什么?</font>
What? -The vaudeville, what do you think?

1319
02:17:19,640 --> 02:17:21,140
<font size=24>是的!</font>
Yes.

1320
02:17:21,520 --> 02:17:23,730
<font size=24>-我能看看吗?  -不能!</font>
-Can I see it? -No.

1321
02:17:25,150 --> 02:17:26,940
<font size=24>为什么不能?</font>
Why not?

1322
02:17:27,150 --> 02:17:29,780
<font size=24>因为没有什么可看</font>
Because there's nothing to see.

1323
02:17:38,120 --> 02:17:39,660
<font size=24>听着</font>
Look...

1324
02:17:40,620 --> 02:17:46,630
<font size=24>你说下礼拜可排演的</font>
I asked you if we could start rehearsals next week and you said yes.

1325
02:17:47,880 --> 02:17:52,260
<font size=24>可以呀!  在那儿?  让我看看</font>
-Well, we can. -So let me see it. Where is it?

1326
02:17:53,050 --> 02:17:54,760
<font size=24>这</font>
Here.

1327
02:17:55,680 --> 02:18:01,180
<font size=24>全在我脑子里  剩下的只要把他写下来</font>
It's all right here in my noodle. The rest is just scribbling.

1328
02:18:01,390 --> 02:18:05,190
<font size=24>喝酒及把它写下来  喝酒及把它写下来</font>
Scribbling and bibbling. Bibbling and scribbling.

1329
02:18:08,190 --> 02:18:10,690
<font size=24>-你想喝点东西吗?  -你这小子</font>
-Like a drink? -Look, you little clown!

1330
02:18:10,900 --> 02:18:13,570
<font size=24>你知道我雇了多少人</font>
Do you know how many people I've hired?

1331
02:18:13,820 --> 02:18:16,280
<font size=24>-放开他  -我要付钱给人家!</font>
-Leave him alone! -I'm paying them!

1332
02:18:16,530 --> 02:18:20,830
<font size=24>-他已尽他的全力了  -我付钱而却来等你写完曲子  真荒谬</font>
-He's doing his best. -Paying them to wait. It's ridiculous!

1333
02:18:21,040 --> 02:18:23,830
<font size=24>你知道什么叫荒谬吗?  你的剧本</font>
You know what's ridiculous? Your libretto!

1334
02:18:24,040 --> 02:18:25,040
<font size=24>是吗?</font>
Oh!

1335
02:18:25,210 --> 02:18:27,880
<font size=24>只有白痴才会要这种剧本</font>
Only an idiot would ask him to work on that!

1336
02:18:28,090 --> 02:18:30,670
<font size=24>弄蛇的摩笆</font>
Twelve-foot snakes, magic flutes?

1337
02:18:30,880 --> 02:18:33,720
<font size=24>那么写安魂曲又有多高明</font>
What's so intelligent about a Requiem?

1338
02:18:33,930 --> 02:18:36,890
<font size=24>钱!  钱!</font>
Money. Money.

1339
02:18:39,810 --> 02:18:41,560
<font size=24>疯了!</font>
You're mad.

1340
02:18:42,230 --> 02:18:43,680
<font size=24>显然她也疯了</font>
She's mad.

1341
02:18:44,060 --> 02:18:48,230
<font size=24>写下来  兄弟!  把你的灵感写下</font>
-Oh, yes? -Wolfie, write it down.

1342
02:18:48,440 --> 02:18:50,400
<font size=24>写下来</font>
Just write it down.

1343
02:18:50,570 --> 02:18:52,690
<font size=24>写在纸上</font>
On paper.

1344
02:18:52,900 --> 02:18:56,070
<font size=24>在你的脑中根本没有用</font>
It's no use to anybody in your head.

1345
02:18:56,240 --> 02:19:00,120
<font size=24>去你的  安魂曲</font>
To hell with your death Mass!

1346
02:19:00,830 --> 02:19:03,580
<font size=24>冷静!  你是怎么了</font>
Calm yourself. What's the matter with you?

1347
02:19:03,830 --> 02:19:07,120
<font size=24>-我不再到那儿工作了  -为什么?  发生什么事?</font>
-I won't work there anymore. -What happened?

1348
02:19:08,380 --> 02:19:11,420
<font size=24>你不知道是怎么一回事</font>
You don't know what it's like.

1349
02:19:11,590 --> 02:19:14,630
<font size=24>莫扎特令我害怕</font>
Herr Mozart frightens me.

1350
02:19:14,880 --> 02:19:16,630
<font size=24>他整天喝酒</font>
He drinks all day...

1351
02:19:16,890 --> 02:19:20,600
<font size=24>并且吃药  使他变得更糟</font>
then takes all that medicine and it makes him worse.

1352
02:19:20,760 --> 02:19:22,260
<font size=24>他有没有在工作?</font>
Is he working?

1353
02:19:24,060 --> 02:19:27,140
<font size=24>我好怕  真的!</font>
Oh, I am frightened, sir, really!

1354
02:19:27,400 --> 02:19:32,270
<font size=24>-当他讲话时  根本就是胡言乱语  -他有没有在工作?</font>
-When he speaks, he makes no sense. -Is he working?

1355
02:19:34,150 --> 02:19:36,450
<font size=24>我想有吧!</font>
I suppose so.

1356
02:19:36,950 --> 02:19:41,620
<font size=24>他常坐下来写什么歌剧的</font>
He sits there all the time, doing some silly opera.

1357
02:19:41,870 --> 02:19:45,000
<font size=24>-歌剧?  -求求你别再叫我回去</font>
-Opera? -Don't ask me to go back again.

1358
02:19:45,250 --> 02:19:48,460
<font size=24>我好怕!  我真的好怕</font>
I'm frightened. I'm very, very frightened!

1359
02:19:48,670 --> 02:19:51,880
<font size=24>你确定是歌剧吗?</font>
Are you sure it's an opera?

1360
02:21:35,360 --> 02:21:37,940
<font size=24>我还没有作完</font>
I don't have it yet.

1361
02:21:38,490 --> 02:21:41,610
<font size=24>你答应了我的要求了吗?</font>
Are you neglecting my request?

1362
02:21:42,280 --> 02:21:45,410
<font size=24>不..哦...</font>
No. No, I....

1363
02:21:46,330 --> 02:21:48,620
<font size=24>我答应过你</font>
I promise you...

1364
02:21:48,830 --> 02:21:52,830
<font size=24>要给你写一个好歌剧的</font>
I'll give you a wonderful piece, the best I ever

1365
02:21:56,590 --> 02:21:59,920
<font size=24>这是我太太</font>
This is my wife, Stanzi.

1366
02:22:00,470 --> 02:22:04,090
<font size=24>我已工作了一整夜  对吗?</font>
I've been sick, but I'm all right now, aren't I?

1367
02:22:04,300 --> 02:22:06,430
<font size=24>是的  没错</font>
Yes, sir. He's all right.

1368
02:22:06,600 --> 02:22:09,770
<font size=24>而他也很辛苦的在工作</font>
And he's working on it very hard.

1369
02:22:10,930 --> 02:22:14,600
<font size=24>我还需要两个星期  求求你</font>
Give me two more weeks. Please.

1370
02:22:14,810 --> 02:22:19,110
<font size=24>我会尽力完成它的  我保证!</font>
The sooner you finish, the greater your reward.

1371
02:22:19,360 --> 02:22:21,440
<font size=24>去完成把</font>
Work.

1372
02:22:30,290 --> 02:22:31,830
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Wolfie.

1373
02:22:34,120 --> 02:22:37,290
<font size=24>我想你是真的发疯了</font>
I think you really are going mad.

1374
02:22:38,800 --> 02:22:43,380
<font size=24>你替那白痴演员作得像个下奴  而他却分文末付</font>
You slave for that idiot actor who won't give you a penny!

1375
02:22:43,630 --> 02:22:46,390
<font size=24>而这个人  他不是个鬼</font>
And here, this is not a ghost!

1376
02:22:46,640 --> 02:22:50,640
<font size=24>他是个活生生的人且付你钱</font>
This is a real man, who puts down real money.

1377
02:22:52,640 --> 02:22:55,640
<font size=24>你为何不完成它呢?</font>
Why on earth won't you finish it?

1378
02:22:56,600 --> 02:23:00,400
<font size=24>你能给我个我能了解的理由吗?</font>
Can you give me one reason I can understand?

1379
02:23:02,490 --> 02:23:04,610
<font size=24>他这么作是在杀我</font>
It's killing me.

1380
02:23:08,490 --> 02:23:10,830
<font size=24>你醉了!  对不对?</font>
You're drunk, aren't you?

1381
02:23:10,990 --> 02:23:14,040
<font size=24>萝拉说你一直在喝酒</font>
Be honest, tell me. You've been drinking.

1382
02:23:16,830 --> 02:23:21,630
<font size=24>太不公平了  我一天到晚都在担心你</font>
It's not fair. I worry about you all the time.

1383
02:23:22,050 --> 02:23:25,420
<font size=24>尽一切力量来帮助你</font>
I do everything I can to help you.

1384
02:23:25,680 --> 02:23:30,010
<font size=24>而你却只会喝酒  胡言乱语  和吓我</font>
And all you do is drink and talk nonsense and frighten me.

1385
02:23:30,220 --> 02:23:32,720
<font size=24>你回床上去吧!</font>
Go back to bed!

1386
02:23:42,030 --> 02:23:43,570
<font size=24>求你了</font>
Please.

1387
02:23:44,690 --> 02:23:48,570
<font size=24>我宁可坐在此</font>
Let me.... Let me sit here.

1388
02:23:51,580 --> 02:23:53,700
<font size=24>跟你坐在此</font>
Let me stay here with you.

1389
02:26:27,320 --> 02:26:30,070
<font size=24>我作的  我为此感到骄做</font>
I did it. And I was proud to do it.

1390
02:26:30,320 --> 02:26:34,240
<font size=24>我告诉她说  走吧!  带着孩子一道走吧!</font>
"Leave!" I said. "Right away. Take the child with you!

1391
02:26:34,450 --> 02:26:38,950
<font size=24>这儿有钱去那间修养所去  寻回你的健康吧!  令人吃惊</font>
Go to the spa and get your health back." I was shocked.

1392
02:26:39,200 --> 02:26:41,950
<font size=24>令人吃惊当看到她变成那种模样</font>
Shocked to my foundation when I saw her.

1393
02:26:42,210 --> 02:26:45,540
<font size=24>可怜的孩子我不敢相信我的眼睛</font>
I couldn't believe my eyes, poor little thing.

1394
02:26:45,710 --> 02:26:49,210
<font size=24>你这个魔鬼  没人比得上你  是不是</font>
You monster! No one exists but you, do they?

1395
02:26:49,380 --> 02:26:52,050
<font size=24>你和你的音乐  我警告过她</font>
You and your music. I warned her.

1396
02:26:52,260 --> 02:26:55,090
<font size=24>选个男子汉  不要选个小孩</font>
"Choose a man, not a baby," I said.

1397
02:26:55,340 --> 02:27:00,470
<font size=24>如她嫁给你  一生不幸  你这自私的东西</font>
"You marry him, you won't have a pot to piss in." You selfish thing!

1398
02:27:00,720 --> 02:27:04,640
<font size=24>你这自私的东西你听见了吗?</font>
Selfish, that's what you are. Simply selfish! Do you hear me?

1399
02:30:48,700 --> 02:30:49,990
<font size=24>扶他起来</font>
Pick him up.

1400
02:30:50,200 --> 02:30:51,950
<font size=24>把他扶起来</font>
Pick him up!

1401
02:30:53,960 --> 02:30:56,370
<font size=24>小心  过来帮忙!</font>
Be careful. Come with me.

1402
02:30:56,630 --> 02:30:58,380
<font size=24>你跟我来</font>
You, follow me.

1403
02:31:25,990 --> 02:31:29,660
<font size=24>结束了吗?  结束了</font>
-Is it over? -Yes, it's over. It's over.

1404
02:31:31,160 --> 02:31:32,620
<font size=24>走!</font>
Go!

1405
02:32:14,450 --> 02:32:16,200
<font size=24>走吧!  走!  走!</font>
Go, go. go.

1406
02:32:17,210 --> 02:32:19,080
<font size=24>走!  走!</font>
Go! Go!

1407
02:32:47,990 --> 02:32:49,950
<font size=24>你太太呢?</font>
Where is your wife?

1408
02:32:53,120 --> 02:32:55,580
<font size=24>你太太呢?</font>
Where is your wife?

1409
02:32:57,910 --> 02:33:02,080
<font size=24>她身体不好  去休养处了</font>
She's not well either. She went to the spa.

1410
02:33:03,460 --> 02:33:05,800
<font size=24>你对我真好</font>
You are so good to me.

1411
02:33:06,300 --> 02:33:09,340
<font size=24>我非常感谢你</font>
Truly. Thank you.

1412
02:33:09,800 --> 02:33:11,630
<font size=24>不要!  请你不要挂意</font>
Please!

1413
02:33:12,340 --> 02:33:16,430
<font size=24>真高兴你来看我的歌剧</font>
No, I mean to come to my opera.

1414
02:33:16,600 --> 02:33:21,600
<font size=24>你  你是唯一来的我的朋友</font>
You. You are the only colleague of mine who came.

1415
02:33:24,610 --> 02:33:26,440
<font size=24>莫扎特</font>
Mozart.

1416
02:33:27,610 --> 02:33:31,320
<font size=24>我从不错过你写的任何作品</font>
I would never miss anything you had written.

1417
02:33:31,860 --> 02:33:35,280
<font size=24>-都是些小儿科  -不  不!</font>
-It's just a vaudeville. -No, no!

1418
02:33:35,490 --> 02:33:37,450
<font size=24>超绝的作品</font>
It's a sublime piece.

1419
02:33:38,750 --> 02:33:40,830
<font size=24>祟高的作品</font>
The grandest operone!

1420
02:33:49,970 --> 02:33:51,760
<font size=24>我告诉你</font>
I tell you...

1421
02:33:52,260 --> 02:33:56,180
<font size=24>你是我所知的最伟大的作曲家</font>
you are the greatest composer known to me.

1422
02:34:00,270 --> 02:34:01,520
<font size=24>真的?</font>
Do you mean it?

1423
02:34:07,570 --> 02:34:09,400
<font size=24>是他!  是谁?</font>
-It's him! -Who?

1424
02:34:10,030 --> 02:34:11,690
<font size=24>那个人</font>
The man.

1425
02:34:12,200 --> 02:34:13,990
<font size=24>他来了</font>
He's here.

1426
02:34:17,030 --> 02:34:19,080
<font size=24>叫他走开!</font>
Tell him to go away.

1427
02:34:19,330 --> 02:34:23,580
<font size=24>告诉他我有事别让他进来</font>
Tell him I'm still working on it. Don't let him in.

1428
02:34:24,420 --> 02:34:26,670
<font size=24>不  等等!</font>
No, no. Wait!

1429
02:34:26,880 --> 02:34:30,880
<font size=24>问问他现在能给我一些钱吗?</font>
Ask him if he would give me some money now.

1430
02:34:31,090 --> 02:34:34,680
<font size=24>告诉他  如果他给  我就会帮他完成</font>
Tell him if he would, it will help me to finish it.

1431
02:34:53,570 --> 02:34:55,910
<font size=24>萨列里!  是的</font>
-Salieri? -Yes.

1432
02:34:57,830 --> 02:35:01,700
<font size=24>-他在吗?  -他在睡觉</font>
-Can we come in? -Better not. He's sleeping.

1433
02:35:02,540 --> 02:35:06,420
<font size=24>我知道他晕倒了  他还好吗?</font>
-He's all right, though? -Yes, he's just exhausted.

1434
02:35:06,630 --> 02:35:09,750
<font size=24>是的他只是太累了  头昏昏的</font>
He became dizzy, that's all.

1435
02:35:09,960 --> 02:35:14,470
<font size=24>-告诉他我们来过好吗?  -好的</font>
-Well, tell him we came by, won't you? -Of course.

1436
02:35:14,930 --> 02:35:18,090
<font size=24>给他这个  他的报酬</font>
Give him this. That's his share.

1437
02:35:18,970 --> 02:35:21,720
<font size=24>这会使他高兴  当然!</font>
-That should cheer him up. -Indeed!

1438
02:35:21,890 --> 02:35:25,350
<font size=24>各位晚安!  真的是...</font>
And now, good night to you all. It was...

1439
02:35:25,560 --> 02:35:27,440
<font size=24>...完美之作</font>
perfection, truly.

1440
02:35:27,650 --> 02:35:29,110
<font size=24>怎么样?</font>
Thank you.

1441
02:35:39,740 --> 02:35:41,580
<font size=24>怎么回事?</font>
What happened?

1442
02:35:49,960 --> 02:35:52,630
<font size=24>他说给你这个</font>
He said to give you this.

1443
02:35:53,510 --> 02:35:56,800
<font size=24>如果你明晚之前能完成</font>
And if you finish by tomorrow night...

1444
02:35:57,760 --> 02:36:00,760
<font size=24>它将会付你另外100元</font>
he will pay you another hundred ducats.

1445
02:36:01,430 --> 02:36:02,930
<font size=24>另外的...?</font>
Another...?

1446
02:36:03,770 --> 02:36:06,810
<font size=24>那太赶了  明天晚上!</font>
That's too soon. Tomorrow night....

1447
02:36:08,600 --> 02:36:10,520
<font size=24>不可能!</font>
It's impossible.

1448
02:36:13,900 --> 02:36:16,940
<font size=24>-他说1OO元?  -是的</font>
-Did he say a hundred? -Yes.

1449
02:36:22,530 --> 02:36:24,490
<font size=24>太赶了!</font>
It's too soon.

1450
02:36:26,790 --> 02:36:28,500
<font size=24>我能否...</font>
Can I...?

1451
02:36:28,960 --> 02:36:30,960
<font size=24>我能帮你忙吗?</font>
Could I help you?

1452
02:36:33,550 --> 02:36:35,420
<font size=24>你会吗?</font>
Would you?

1453
02:36:39,130 --> 02:36:40,640
<font size=24>事实上你能的</font>
Actually, you could.

1454
02:36:48,230 --> 02:36:50,810
<font size=24>我要走!  去哪儿</font>
-I want to go. -Where?

1455
02:36:51,150 --> 02:36:54,360
<font size=24>-我要回去维也那!  -现在?</font>
-I want to go back to Vienna.  Now?

1456
02:36:54,570 --> 02:36:56,150
<font size=24>-是的!  -为什么?</font>
Yes. Why?

1457
02:36:58,570 --> 02:37:00,320
<font size=24>我觉得不对</font>
I feel wrong.

1458
02:37:01,870 --> 02:37:04,370
<font size=24>我觉得在这里不大对</font>
I feel wrong being here.

1459
02:37:07,250 --> 02:37:10,870
<font size=24>在什么地方停了  在Recordare(乐曲章节名)的结尾</font>
-Where did I stop? -The end of the Recordare.

1460
02:37:11,080 --> 02:37:12,710
<font size=24>下面是Confutatis(乐曲章节名)...</font>
So now Confutatis....

1461
02:37:19,590 --> 02:37:22,010
<font size=24>你怎么翻译这一段歌词</font>
How would you translate that?

1462
02:37:22,180 --> 02:37:25,010
<font size=24>付诸地狱之火</font>
"Consigned to flames of woe."

1463
02:37:27,180 --> 02:37:29,890
<font size=24>-你相信这种说法吗?  -什么?</font>
-Do you believe in it? -What?

1464
02:37:31,190 --> 02:37:35,230
<font size=24>火永不灭  永远燃烧着你</font>
A fire which never dies, burning you forever.

1465
02:37:36,570 --> 02:37:37,860
<font size=24>恩</font>
Oh, yes.

1466
02:37:39,530 --> 02:37:41,200
<font size=24>也许吧</font>
Possible.

1467
02:37:42,870 --> 02:37:46,700
<font size=24>-来吧  让我们开始继续作曲  -我们在降F大调停止</font>
-Come, let's begin. -We ended in F major.

1468
02:37:46,910 --> 02:37:50,250
<font size=24>接着  降A小调</font>
-Yes. -So, now, A minor.

1469
02:37:58,050 --> 02:38:01,090
<font size=24>-A小调!  -是的</font>
-A minor. -Yes.

1470
02:38:03,930 --> 02:38:06,930
<font size=24>Confutatis(乐曲章节名)部分  A小调</font>
Confutatis. A minor.

1471
02:38:09,220 --> 02:38:11,140
<font size=24>开始声乐部分</font>
Start with the voices.

1472
02:38:11,390 --> 02:38:14,650
<font size=24>-由男低音开始  进入第二节  -时间是?</font>
-Basses first. Second beat of the -Time?

1473
02:38:14,900 --> 02:38:18,440
<font size=24>通常的时间  第一节第二拍的时候</font>
Common time. Second beat of the first measure.

1474
02:38:19,820 --> 02:38:21,780
<font size=24>在A小调</font>
On A.

1475
02:38:23,660 --> 02:38:25,910
<font size=24>第二节第二拍</font>
Second measure, second beat.

1476
02:38:26,660 --> 02:38:27,910
<font size=24>你知道吗?</font>
You see?

1477
02:38:28,120 --> 02:38:29,910
<font size=24>-G调?  -当然</font>
-Yes. G-sharp? -Of course.

1478
02:38:30,120 --> 02:38:33,410
<font size=24>再来第三节第二拍  E调</font>
Second beat of the third measure, on E.

1479
02:38:40,420 --> 02:38:42,760
<font size=24>记下来了吗?  给我看看</font>
Do you have me? Show me.

1480
02:39:02,490 --> 02:39:05,110
<font size=24>很好  很好</font>
Good. Good.

1481
02:39:05,280 --> 02:39:06,860
<font size=24>现在男高音部分</font>
Now the tenors.

